{"name": "commitment", "metadata": {"name": "commitment", "version": "4.0.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/chris48s/commitment", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests"], "summary": "An incomplete Python 3 wrapper for the GitHub API", "upload_time": 1732823703}, "documentation": ["# commitment\n\n[![Run tests](https://github.com/chris48s/commitment/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg?branch=master)](https://github.com/chris48s/commitment/actions/workflows/test.yml)\n[![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/chris48s/commitment/branch/master/graph/badge.svg?token=4BL8HL7913)](https://codecov.io/gh/chris48s/commitment)\n![PyPI Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/commitment.svg)\n![License](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/commitment.svg)\n![Python Compatibility](https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json?query=info.requires_python&label=python&url=https%3A%2F%2Fpypi.org%2Fpypi%2Fcommitment%2Fjson)\n![Code style: black](https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20style-black-000000.svg)\n\nAn incomplete Python 3 wrapper for the [GitHub API](https://developer.github.com/v3/).\n\nNote this project does not aim to provide a complete abstraction over the GitHub API - just a few high-level convenience methods for pushing data to a GitHub repo.\n\n## Installation\n\n`pip install commitment`\n\n## Usage\n\nGenerate a GitHub API key: https://github.com/settings/tokens\n\n```python\nfrom commitment import GitHubCredentials, GitHubClient\n\ncredentials = GitHubCredentials(\n    repo=\"myuser/somerepo\",\n    name=\"myuser\",\n    email=\"someone@example.com\",\n    api_key=\"f00b42\",\n)\n\nclient = GitHubClient(credentials)\n\nclient.create_branch('my_new_branch', base_branch='master')\nclient.push_file('Hello World!', 'directory/filename.txt', 'my commit message', branch='my_new_branch')\nclient.open_pull_request('my_new_branch', 'title', 'body', base_branch='master')\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "commitment", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "commitment.GitHubClient", "xref": {"fqname": "commitment.commitment.GitHubClient", "project": null}}, {"name": "commitment.GitHubCredentials", "xref": {"fqname": "commitment.commitment.GitHubCredentials", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "commitment.commitment", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "commitment.commitment.force_bytes", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "data", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "encoding", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "commitment.commitment.GitHubCredentials", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "commitment.commitment.GitHubCredentials.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "repo", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "email", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "api_key", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "commitment.commitment.GitHubClient", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "commitment.commitment.GitHubClient.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "credentials", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "commitment.commitment.GitHubClient._request", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "method", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "url", "type": null, "default": nul